---
name: Cisco ISE syslog → OCSF
description: |
  Listens for Cisco ISE remote-target syslog over TCP, parses the events, and
  maps them to OCSF. `read_syslog` leaves the `CISE_<Category>` tag at the start
  of `content`, so the parser recovers the category from the message body.
---

from_tcp "0.0.0.0:514" {
  read_syslog
}
cisco::ise::parse message=content
cisco::ise::ocsf::map
ocsf::derive
ocsf::cast
publish "ocsf"
